snippet.title: Amber Heard admitting violence
snippet.description:
Recording of Amber Heard belittling Johnny Depp and admitting to hitting him, while calling him a baby. In July 2020 the Daily Mail reported this as a secret recording of Amber by Johnny, released by his legal team during the 2020 High Court trial so part of it is used here, along with public domain images, under fair usage, with thanks.
Transcript to be included in the forthcoming update of the book, 'Abuse - Monster in the House'. 
Decide for yourselves who is the real victim and real abuser here.
